#etcsl: line-id=D.25

D.26. gal-an-zu {d}en-lil₂-le igi ŋal₂-la-ni-še₃# [... ...] UN zid-de₃-eš [...]
#lem: galanzu[wise]; Enlil[1]DN; igi[eye]; ŋal[⟦be⟧ to be (there]; X; X; X; zid[right]; X
#etcsl: line-id=D.26

D.27. lugal-ŋu₁₀ diŋir nam tar-ra ki ur₅ sag₉-ge [...]
